Gatara/Riekan/Jayde::

"Hey, they're on the run!" Jayde cries out jubilantly as she watches 
the Maximal group retreat.

"We've got to leave as well," Gatara points out.  "Torin sent me a 
priority alert - someone's found Rogue Star, and he knows about the 
girl."

"Aw, slag it!" Jayde pouts.  "I was hoping for a chance to flirt with 
someone new for a change."

Jayde and Riekan shift over to robot form and follow their leader 
back to base.
